<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - mn ạlnhạrdẗ nfsy msẖ mlky nfsy mlkk yạ yswʿ

[V2]
 wḥdk ạnt ạlʿạrf qymty ạmtlkny yạ yswʿ

[V3]
 1- mḥṣwr wsṭ ạlḥjạrẗ bạṣrkẖ wkly ạnyyn

[V4]
 bạsʿy lạdẖyẗ nfsy wʿạysẖ dymạ ḥzyn

[V5]
 dymạ bạhyn nfsy mʿ syd qạsy rdỷ qydny bạlslạsl ạfqdny kl sẖỷ

[V6]
 wdạlwqt lmạ sẖwftk yạyswʿ ḥsyt bqymẗ nfsy ạlly ḍạʿt mny

[V7]
 dh ạnạ ʿsẖt bʿyd ʿnk fy qswẗ wdmwʿ lkn rạjʿ wbạqwlk ḥrrny wạmtlkny

[V8]
 2- fạqd mʿny ạlḥyạẗ wạkẖd nfsy llmwt

[V9]
 mjnwn bạsʿy lḍyạʿy wlạsạmʿ ạy ṣwt

[V10]
